WEBVTT

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:15.060
I've told you to leave Caisheng.
Why are you hesitating?

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:18.260
I've been here for so many years.

00:00:18.260 --> 00:00:21.019
I have a lot of things to handle
before I resign.

00:00:22.339 --> 00:00:24.059
Don't blame me for speaking harshly.

00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:25.749
(Xie Kaiyan)
That position Meng Guangcai

00:00:25.749 --> 00:00:27.199
(Deputy Head of Beiyan Commercial Bank)
arranged for you is just for show.

00:00:27.199 --> 00:00:30.140
You're just his public face.
What real tasks could there be?

00:00:33.340 --> 00:00:36.200
Uncle, you're well-informed
and have connections.

00:00:37.119 --> 00:00:38.780
What's going on with him?

00:00:39.799 --> 00:00:41.859
Wait, why do you still care about him?

00:00:45.619 --> 00:00:47.340
The police keeps things confidentially.

00:00:48.560 --> 00:00:51.240
As a bank head,
I do have broad connections.

00:00:51.619 --> 00:00:53.439
But I still haven't found out anything.

00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:59.399
I asked you here today to tell you

00:00:59.759 --> 00:01:02.240
not to involve yourself
in Meng Guangcai's affairs.

00:01:02.439 --> 00:01:06.060
I got you into their company
just to let you collect a paycheck

00:01:06.060 --> 00:01:07.560
and to monitor their operations.

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:10.579
Look what you've done!
You even had his kid.

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:14.239
You've known him
since he started his business.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.939
He couldn't be in serious trouble,
could he?

00:01:18.180 --> 00:01:19.480
How would I know?

00:01:21.579 --> 00:01:23.540
Anyway, we suspect
he might've offended someone.

00:01:26.120 --> 00:01:29.579
But with no news for days,
they probably haven't found anything.

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:33.439
Then there's no need for me
to leave Caisheng now.

00:01:33.799 --> 00:01:36.760
Wait, you're engaging in finance.
Are you really that clueless?

00:01:38.579 --> 00:01:41.180
Caisheng has expanded
from real estate to finance.

00:01:41.439 --> 00:01:42.819
Its operations are sprawling.

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:45.939
Think of how much money
and how many people are involved!

00:01:47.540 --> 00:01:49.900
Even if they can't convict him now,

00:01:49.900 --> 00:01:52.219
a few more days of digging
could uncover something.

00:01:52.219 --> 00:01:53.799
Then you and I will get implicated.

00:01:55.260 --> 00:01:56.620
Tell me the truth.

00:01:57.760 --> 00:02:00.819
Has Meng Guangcai
embezzled Caisheng's funds?

00:03:12.986 --> 00:03:16.288
=The Silent Rift=

00:03:16.288 --> 00:03:19.066
=Episode 5=
(Money Laundry)

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:22.360
Get me a doctor.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:27.520
Get me a doctor! I'm in pain!

00:03:28.120 --> 00:03:29.300
Get me a doctor!

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:31.120
Wang Dazhu!

00:03:31.120 --> 00:03:31.900
Behave!

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:34.099
I want a doctor!

00:03:37.819 --> 00:03:38.520
Master.

00:03:40.860 --> 00:03:42.099
How did you sneak out?

00:03:43.460 --> 00:03:46.460
Sneak out? That sounds terrible.

00:03:47.860 --> 00:03:49.520
Chief Liu told me

00:03:51.800 --> 00:03:54.400
not to let you be involved
in the investigation anymore.

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:57.439
He wants you to rest
and recuperate at home.

00:03:57.439 --> 00:04:00.120
If there's any problem,
you can just offer us suggestions.

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:02.620
I know. I'll definitely
do as Chief Liu said.

00:04:03.080 --> 00:04:05.319
I'll just offer suggestions.
You guys go ahead.

00:04:08.860 --> 00:04:09.599
Captain Li.

00:04:19.459 --> 00:04:19.959
Master.

00:04:20.439 --> 00:04:24.660
Shouldn't our focus be on
investigating Meng Guangcai?

00:04:24.959 --> 00:04:27.319
Yet, you brought in Wang Dazhu.

00:04:27.480 --> 00:04:31.939
We have no evidence
linking Wang Dazhu to the 6.10 case.

00:04:32.139 --> 00:04:33.220
Isn't it causing trouble?

00:04:33.319 --> 00:04:36.660
Look at Wang Dazhu.
He doesn't say a word.

00:04:37.920 --> 00:04:39.139
Team Leader Zhang, look.

00:04:39.720 --> 00:04:41.720
Wang Dazhu doesn't say a word now.

00:04:42.639 --> 00:04:43.420
But,

00:04:44.139 --> 00:04:47.100
precisely that silence speaks volumes.

00:04:48.220 --> 00:04:50.439
Silence doesn't prove anything.

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:52.540
The evidence is right here.

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:54.699
Meng Guangcai is a strong suspect.

00:04:55.220 --> 00:04:56.480
Now we need to get details

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:58.339
about his accomplices from him.

00:05:00.939 --> 00:05:02.319
If you want evidence,

00:05:02.779 --> 00:05:05.639
we have DNA evidence from the 6.10 case.

00:05:06.040 --> 00:05:07.420
But Meng Guangcai doesn't know it.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:10.279
After coming in, he could say nothing.

00:05:10.540 --> 00:05:14.040
For him, maintaining silence or actively

00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:16.339
revealing Zuo Long
and Ma Zhongwu's details to us,

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:19.100
which option benefits him more,
Captain Li?

00:05:20.420 --> 00:05:22.220
Maintaining silence, of course.

00:05:22.379 --> 00:05:24.819
See? Captain Li analyzed it perfectly.

00:05:25.759 --> 00:05:28.600
Let me share my amateur analysis
with you both.

00:05:29.839 --> 00:05:32.220
Meng Guangcai, though tight-lipped,

00:05:32.339 --> 00:05:34.480
hasn't held back on
revealing necessary information.

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:35.819
And it's very detailed.

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:38.100
What he did, when it was
and where he was

00:05:38.100 --> 00:05:40.220
in 1993, he wrote it all down.

00:05:40.759 --> 00:05:43.939
He even wrote down details
about meeting me.

00:05:43.980 --> 00:05:45.720
He's just trying to prove his innocence.

00:05:46.600 --> 00:05:50.100
He knows verifying his whereabouts
from ten or twenty years ago

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.939
is extremely difficult.

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:52.980
Wrong.

00:05:53.819 --> 00:05:54.759
It's very convenient.

00:05:55.920 --> 00:05:59.779
I have the investigation notes
from the 6.10 robbery case in 1993.

00:06:00.839 --> 00:06:01.759
I have them all here.

00:06:05.339 --> 00:06:08.339
I have the Jinwan Market construction
site investigation notes in 1993.

00:06:08.920 --> 00:06:12.060
I have the Beiyan Railway Passenger
Section investigation notes in 1993.

00:06:12.379 --> 00:06:15.500
I also have the Beiyan Train Station
investigation notes

00:06:15.500 --> 00:06:16.500
in 1993.

00:06:16.500 --> 00:06:20.540
And I have the personnel screening notes
from Beiyan construction sites in 1993.

00:06:22.540 --> 00:06:23.439
Great!

00:06:23.660 --> 00:06:26.920
Zhou, come on. Let's pull out
all the relevant materials.

00:06:26.920 --> 00:06:27.500
- Yes.
- Go.

00:06:39.379 --> 00:06:41.500
(6.10 City Credit Union Robbery)
Right after the robbery,

00:06:42.540 --> 00:06:45.980
I questioned Meng Guangcai.

00:06:46.720 --> 00:06:50.160
This is the interrogation notes
from that time.

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:52.420
It's also his alibi from back then.

00:06:53.339 --> 00:06:55.160
I printed a few copies for you.

00:06:55.939 --> 00:06:56.819
On June 9th,

00:06:58.319 --> 00:07:01.184
Meng Guangcai came to Jinwan City,
looking for construction site work.

00:07:01.319 --> 00:07:04.339
On June 10th,
he met with the site manager.

00:07:04.600 --> 00:07:06.160
They couldn't agree on the wages.

00:07:06.779 --> 00:07:09.100
On June 11th, he returned to Beiyan.

00:07:09.879 --> 00:07:11.600
I verified all the places he mentioned,

00:07:11.839 --> 00:07:15.480
including the construction site
and the train station.

00:07:17.100 --> 00:07:19.259
So you suspected him that early on?

00:07:20.040 --> 00:07:21.259
Putting in so much effort?

00:07:22.220 --> 00:07:26.439
I aimed to investigate
every detail thoroughly,

00:07:26.819 --> 00:07:29.040
striving for perfection,
accuracy, and rigor.

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:30.759
I wasn't actually suspecting him.

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:33.600
So what were the results back then?

00:07:33.839 --> 00:07:36.819
Look, everything matches up.

00:07:37.540 --> 00:07:39.424
At the construction site
and the train station,

00:07:39.540 --> 00:07:42.540
every single person remembered
a guy named Meng Guangcai.

00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:44.319
So after all that,

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:47.000
you proved his alibi?

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:49.040
Wait a minute.

00:07:49.600 --> 00:07:51.600
If he has an alibi,

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:53.980
then how did the DNA at the scene match?

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:55.379
Actually, this shows

00:07:55.879 --> 00:07:57.540
that Meng Guangcai crafted

00:07:57.600 --> 00:08:00.160
a near-perfect alibi.

00:08:00.920 --> 00:08:01.660
Liu,

00:08:02.220 --> 00:08:04.779
bring me his interrogation records
from the past two days.

00:08:05.100 --> 00:08:06.220
Officer Zhu, here.

00:08:08.759 --> 00:08:11.040
How could so many people collaborate?

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:12.339
It's entirely possible.

00:08:12.980 --> 00:08:14.500
The site manager back then

00:08:14.500 --> 00:08:16.672
had an argument with him,
and even got into a fight.

00:08:17.319 --> 00:08:19.339
At the train station,
he bumped into a staff member

00:08:19.600 --> 00:08:20.759
and spilled the noodles

00:08:20.759 --> 00:08:21.480
all over himself.

00:08:21.980 --> 00:08:23.980
Everyone remembered him.

00:08:24.660 --> 00:08:26.839
Don't forget it's been twenty years.

00:08:26.839 --> 00:08:28.660
Twenty years! Almost twenty years!

00:08:29.040 --> 00:08:32.039
The two interrogation records
are almost identical,

00:08:32.480 --> 00:08:34.100
and all the details match up.

00:08:34.100 --> 00:08:35.720
They are practically flawless.

00:08:36.840 --> 00:08:37.820
For twenty years.

00:08:38.919 --> 00:08:40.379
Could he remember it that clearly?

00:08:40.980 --> 00:08:42.480
That's what seems suspicious.

00:08:42.659 --> 00:08:44.159
That's what doesn't make sense.

00:08:44.600 --> 00:08:47.080
Alright, suppose you're right.

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:47.899
Then tell me,

00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:50.840
why do you want to arrest Wang Dazhu?

00:08:51.220 --> 00:08:52.279
Arresting Wang Dazhu

00:08:53.340 --> 00:08:56.159
is because I suspect Meng Guangcai
has already made a perfect plan

00:08:56.840 --> 00:08:58.899
and done thorough preparations.

00:08:59.539 --> 00:09:01.580
I want to find a breakthrough
through Wang Dazhu.

00:09:02.340 --> 00:09:04.416
There are
two highly suspicious aspects on it.

00:09:04.416 --> 00:09:07.220
First, this alibi is way too perfect.

00:09:07.779 --> 00:09:09.779
Of course, you could say

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:12.159
Meng Guangcai is a clever criminal.

00:09:12.159 --> 00:09:13.139
Second,

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:15.460
at this very moment, Meng Guangcai

00:09:16.460 --> 00:09:19.159
has revealed Zuo Long and Ma Zhongwu,

00:09:20.100 --> 00:09:21.840
giving us a new direction.

00:09:22.019 --> 00:09:24.100
He's steering us towards
investigating this aspect.

00:09:25.080 --> 00:09:26.340
This is unreasonable.

00:09:27.220 --> 00:09:28.659
For an ordinary person,

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:30.759
an ordinary big boss,

00:09:31.580 --> 00:09:34.379
we could break through his defenses
with interrogation

00:09:34.759 --> 00:09:36.460
and psychological tactics.

00:09:36.460 --> 00:09:39.059
But what we're facing is

00:09:39.539 --> 00:09:42.940
a criminal who has already
made a flawless plan.

00:09:43.700 --> 00:09:48.019
Ordinary interrogation would just be
a waste of time and effort.

00:09:48.759 --> 00:09:52.399
So I brought Wang Dazhu in,
hoping to find a breakthrough with him

00:09:53.019 --> 00:09:54.720
to see if we can uncover anything new

00:09:55.039 --> 00:09:57.840
and their future direction.

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:00.200
Master,

00:10:01.259 --> 00:10:05.139
you keep saying they have a plan.
What exactly is that plan?

00:10:05.379 --> 00:10:07.960
I'm just a cook, I-I don't...

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:09.200
I don't know anything.

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:10.720
You...

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:14.080
I'm just a cook.

00:10:14.779 --> 00:10:16.080
I got Wang Dazhu in here,

00:10:17.320 --> 00:10:20.080
yet you won't even let me see
Wang Dazhu's interrogation video.

00:10:21.659 --> 00:10:22.779
What can I do?

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.960
Get me a doctor! I'm in pain!

00:10:29.759 --> 00:10:30.720
Get me a doctor!

00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:32.399
- Okay, fill that in there.
- Got it.

00:10:32.399 --> 00:10:34.279
Get me a doctor! I'm in pain!

00:10:34.279 --> 00:10:36.320
Master, did you notice anything?

00:10:36.820 --> 00:10:38.000
I wasn't wrong before.

00:10:39.500 --> 00:10:40.840
This guy is an idiot,

00:10:42.539 --> 00:10:44.320
who's been stupid since childhood.

00:10:45.220 --> 00:10:47.779
Master, isn't it obvious?

00:10:48.340 --> 00:10:50.600
When solving cases,
we're not afraid of clever ones.

00:10:51.379 --> 00:10:54.220
Clever ones have lots of ideas,
and too many ideas can lead to chaos.

00:10:55.399 --> 00:10:58.340
But we dread the dumb ones
like this, thick as a brick.

00:10:58.960 --> 00:11:02.220
We couldn't get a word out of him.
This type is hard to deal with.

00:11:02.840 --> 00:11:03.820
Our effort is wasted?

00:11:03.820 --> 00:11:05.259
You didn't notice anything?

00:11:05.580 --> 00:11:07.200
Look at his reaction now.

00:11:08.379 --> 00:11:10.080
Meng Guangcai must've taught him that.

00:11:10.519 --> 00:11:11.960
This guy is a bit simple-minded.

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:14.259
They're afraid he'd reveal something.

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:15.720
Besides,

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:18.720
they're worried his story
doesn't match Meng Guangcai's,

00:11:19.519 --> 00:11:20.940
giving us a breakthrough.

00:11:20.940 --> 00:11:24.600
Right, you're absolutely right. So?

00:11:26.340 --> 00:11:27.840
Stop.

00:11:28.279 --> 00:11:29.220
Stop.

00:11:30.279 --> 00:11:31.960
Rewind. Further back.

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:32.960
Further.

00:11:32.960 --> 00:11:34.779
Slowly.

00:11:35.100 --> 00:11:35.940
Rewind. Stop.

00:11:36.940 --> 00:11:37.720
Zoom in there.

00:11:39.259 --> 00:11:39.960
Zoom in.

00:11:41.519 --> 00:11:42.659
Look at his wrist.

00:11:43.840 --> 00:11:44.940
What's that?

00:11:45.659 --> 00:11:46.720
There's a scar.

00:11:47.340 --> 00:11:48.220
Hard to tell.

00:11:49.200 --> 00:11:51.600
Captain Li, we need tech support.

00:11:51.940 --> 00:11:53.100
Let your tech team

00:11:53.100 --> 00:11:54.460
figure out what this is.

00:11:56.440 --> 00:11:59.159
Give it a shot,
whether it's a long shot or not.

00:11:59.759 --> 00:12:00.779
It might work.

00:12:05.759 --> 00:12:07.279
Liu, come with me.

00:12:07.279 --> 00:12:07.960
Yes.

00:12:33.159 --> 00:12:33.759
Qianqian.

00:12:33.759 --> 00:12:35.960
Yang, where's my dad?

00:12:36.200 --> 00:12:37.779
He is inside. I'll tell him to come.

00:12:38.159 --> 00:12:39.200
Thanks.

00:12:45.940 --> 00:12:46.460
Dad.

00:12:48.580 --> 00:12:49.159
Qianqian.

00:12:49.460 --> 00:12:50.000
Easy.

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:50.879
Silly girl.

00:12:51.519 --> 00:12:53.340
Dad, Mom's really pissed.

00:12:53.340 --> 00:12:54.580
Wait, don't you go to school?

00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:57.340
How can I study
when my dad's gone missing?

00:12:57.639 --> 00:12:59.700
Besides, it's Sunday today.

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:03.580
Dad, I bought you chocolate.

00:13:03.759 --> 00:13:05.879
- Eat it when your blood sugar is low.
- Okay.

00:13:06.080 --> 00:13:09.100
These are medications
to unblock arteries. Take them on time.

00:13:09.220 --> 00:13:10.340
Okay.

00:13:10.700 --> 00:13:13.340
Dad, why don't you come home?

00:13:13.340 --> 00:13:14.460
I'll hold off Mom for you.

00:13:15.100 --> 00:13:17.220
I know. Don't worry.

00:13:18.879 --> 00:13:23.200
Dad, I know you're a hero, a good cop.

00:13:23.940 --> 00:13:25.840
But sometimes you need
to think about me too.

00:13:27.340 --> 00:13:29.820
I know. I won't let my girl worry.

00:13:30.159 --> 00:13:31.100
Alright, Qianqian?

00:13:32.820 --> 00:13:34.639
My dad has been bedridden
for so many years.

00:13:35.460 --> 00:13:37.279
I know you're eager to solve his case.

00:13:39.100 --> 00:13:41.039
But I don't want to lose you, too.

00:13:42.720 --> 00:13:45.759
Look at our Qianqian,
calling this one Dad and that one Dad.

00:13:46.000 --> 00:13:46.820
Sounds confusing.

00:13:46.820 --> 00:13:47.700
I do it on purpose.

00:13:48.220 --> 00:13:51.000
I won't separate you two.
You're both my dads.

00:13:51.840 --> 00:13:52.879
Silly girl.

00:14:08.634 --> 00:14:12.794
(Beiyan County,
Baima Building Materials Market, 1995)

00:14:18.820 --> 00:14:20.519
What is this?

00:14:24.759 --> 00:14:25.500
Guangcai.

00:14:25.700 --> 00:14:28.159
Wait, why are you showing me this stuff?

00:14:32.279 --> 00:14:35.200
I've had enough
of construction site work, right?

00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:37.039
We're different now.

00:14:37.399 --> 00:14:38.519
Here's what I'm thinking.

00:14:39.000 --> 00:14:40.279
We need to find a way

00:14:41.340 --> 00:14:43.500
to spend our savings legitimately.

00:14:44.080 --> 00:14:47.340
Guangcai, you're reading my mind.

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:50.600
Back in Guangnan,
we were stuck in that small hotel,

00:14:50.600 --> 00:14:52.279
and it drove me nuts.

00:14:52.940 --> 00:14:55.100
Not being able to spend the money
makes me frantic.

00:14:56.840 --> 00:14:57.399
Right.

00:14:57.879 --> 00:15:01.159
In that crappy Guangnan hotel,
we met people from all over

00:15:01.720 --> 00:15:03.080
and heard so much business talk.

00:15:03.340 --> 00:15:05.279
Tell me, who were they?

00:15:08.340 --> 00:15:09.259
Who were they?

00:15:10.940 --> 00:15:12.960
Speculators, businessmen.

00:15:13.340 --> 00:15:16.139
Buy low, sell high,
and make quick money flipping stuff.

00:15:19.379 --> 00:15:22.139
So you mean,

00:15:22.279 --> 00:15:24.580
you want to make
quick money flipping stuff?

00:15:26.080 --> 00:15:29.080
Before, we didn't get it.

00:15:30.019 --> 00:15:31.539
We just knew how to build buildings.

00:15:33.379 --> 00:15:36.200
But you know, once a building's up,
people have to live in it,

00:15:36.440 --> 00:15:39.080
and then they need all this stuff.

00:15:39.639 --> 00:15:43.440
Don't underestimate it. Tiles, paint,
and all this building material

00:15:44.259 --> 00:15:45.700
is actually money.

00:15:47.500 --> 00:15:50.019
Do you know who owns
the Baima Building Materials Market now?

00:15:50.700 --> 00:15:51.279
No.

00:15:53.779 --> 00:15:56.460
Remember that Hao guy? What's his name?

00:15:56.700 --> 00:16:00.080
The Hao brothers, those two foremen
from our site back in the day.

00:16:00.080 --> 00:16:02.460
Yes. They've made it big
these last couple years.

00:16:03.340 --> 00:16:06.159
This place is booming now.

00:16:06.159 --> 00:16:08.600
If we want to open a shop here,
we have to get their help.

00:16:08.600 --> 00:16:10.759
Those two are not good people.

00:16:10.759 --> 00:16:13.080
Think back, when you helped
everyone get their wages,

00:16:13.080 --> 00:16:14.200
what did they do?

00:16:14.200 --> 00:16:16.639
They tried every trick
to skim money off the top.

00:16:16.840 --> 00:16:17.940
I hate them.

00:16:18.700 --> 00:16:19.440
Dazhu.

00:16:20.659 --> 00:16:22.000
We're different now.

00:16:22.139 --> 00:16:23.320
We have to move forward.

00:16:23.779 --> 00:16:25.139
Time to change our mindset.

00:16:26.840 --> 00:16:28.840
Let's go find them.

00:16:32.840 --> 00:16:33.440
There they are.

00:16:34.259 --> 00:16:35.259
Got it. Go ahead.

00:16:35.460 --> 00:16:36.019
Okay.

00:16:36.100 --> 00:16:36.840
- Alright.
- Go then.

00:16:37.080 --> 00:16:37.600
Sure thing.

00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:42.259
(Baima Building Materials Market Management)
Sir, may I ask if Mr. Hao is here?

00:16:42.259 --> 00:16:45.019
He is out. You'll have to wait.

00:16:45.539 --> 00:16:46.500
When will he be back?

00:16:48.779 --> 00:16:50.259
This is this year's hottest style.

00:16:50.340 --> 00:16:51.460
Really? Looks pretty good.

00:16:51.460 --> 00:16:53.379
What color do you like?
I can show you around.

00:16:53.379 --> 00:16:54.159
A discount for you.

00:16:54.159 --> 00:16:55.320
- A discount for you.
- We'll look around.

00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:56.000
Alright.

00:16:56.539 --> 00:16:57.659
Okay, feel free to come.

00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:02.899
Sir, when will Mr. Hao be back?

00:17:02.899 --> 00:17:03.440
Please...

00:17:03.440 --> 00:17:04.779
What exactly do you want?

00:17:05.079 --> 00:17:06.640
He has a lot of business to do.

00:17:06.640 --> 00:17:08.380
If you're willing to wait, then wait.

00:17:12.599 --> 00:17:16.059
What's wrong with these guys?
Why putting on airs?

00:17:16.380 --> 00:17:18.420
What should we do?

00:17:19.960 --> 00:17:20.819
Just wait.

00:17:23.440 --> 00:17:24.559
You guys chat, Zhu.

00:17:24.559 --> 00:17:25.519
I'll go make dishes.

00:17:25.519 --> 00:17:26.559
Won't you sit for a bit?

00:17:27.339 --> 00:17:27.960
Mr. Chen.

00:17:28.799 --> 00:17:31.180
Guangcai must have made a fortune
down in Guangnan.

00:17:31.559 --> 00:17:34.460
Otherwise, why would he come back
being secretive and not even tell me?

00:17:34.759 --> 00:17:36.799
I just got back. There's a lot going on.

00:17:36.920 --> 00:17:39.319
Zhu, if you hadn't come,
I would've come to you soon.

00:17:39.559 --> 00:17:42.180
Guangcai, you need
to thank Officer Zhu properly.

00:17:42.420 --> 00:17:45.579
While you were away,
he often came to check on us.

00:17:45.799 --> 00:17:48.880
He's really your good buddy.

00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:49.640
It's only right.

00:17:49.640 --> 00:17:50.720
By the way, Mr. Chen.

00:17:51.220 --> 00:17:53.400
I've been thinking about
what you mentioned last time.

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:58.140
Here are the materials.
Let Yonghui attend night school,

00:17:58.599 --> 00:18:01.900
and then he can get a diploma,
just like going to university.

00:18:02.380 --> 00:18:03.059
Take a look.

00:18:03.900 --> 00:18:04.480
(Beiyan School of Engineering)
Great!

00:18:04.896 --> 00:18:06.140
(Admission Letter)
Zhu, thank you.

00:18:06.440 --> 00:18:07.759
Guangcai, listen.

00:18:08.039 --> 00:18:10.920
Why didn't you tell me about
Yonghui's car accident?

00:18:12.000 --> 00:18:14.220
I could at least help you
find the driver who hit him.

00:18:14.960 --> 00:18:17.140
With an injured arm, he couldn't
take the college entrance exam.

00:18:17.140 --> 00:18:19.279
That's way more important
than you working.

00:18:20.960 --> 00:18:23.700
I thought you're not traffic police.

00:18:23.700 --> 00:18:25.000
This isn't your responsibility.

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:25.680
Yonghui.

00:18:26.460 --> 00:18:28.220
What kind of car was it?
Where did it happen?

00:18:29.099 --> 00:18:30.539
I didn't recognize it.

00:18:30.779 --> 00:18:33.519
What color was it? Black or white?

00:18:33.759 --> 00:18:36.180
Was it on your way to school or home?

00:18:37.140 --> 00:18:37.960
I don't remember.

00:18:39.519 --> 00:18:41.700
Zhu, he was too little back then.

00:18:41.819 --> 00:18:44.720
He was stunned by the impact.
By the time he got up, they were gone.

00:18:46.180 --> 00:18:47.599
Mr. Chen, I'm at fault.

00:18:47.819 --> 00:18:50.200
Back in 1993,
I was completely focused on the case

00:18:50.279 --> 00:18:51.759
and didn't come check on you.

00:18:52.880 --> 00:18:53.920
Zhu, look.

00:18:53.920 --> 00:18:54.779
Guangcai, I...

00:18:54.779 --> 00:18:57.460
You chat. I'll go buy
a couple of cold beers.

00:18:57.460 --> 00:18:58.579
Let's have a proper drink.

00:18:59.779 --> 00:19:00.896
Dazhu, don't buy too much.

00:19:01.160 --> 00:19:02.299
Why is it only one?

00:19:03.059 --> 00:19:03.680
Xue Qin.

00:19:04.319 --> 00:19:05.640
Any beer? Bring some here.

00:19:05.640 --> 00:19:07.940
Zhu and I will drink
till we're drunk today.

00:19:07.960 --> 00:19:09.420
Wait a moment. Let me check.

00:19:10.680 --> 00:19:14.400
Principal Chen and Xiaoliang's
surgeries definitely cost a lot.

00:19:15.220 --> 00:19:17.500
Could you earn enough money
working away all these years?

00:19:20.319 --> 00:19:20.960
Zhu.

00:19:22.420 --> 00:19:23.640
To be honest.

00:19:25.460 --> 00:19:26.720
I don't want to hide it.

00:19:27.700 --> 00:19:32.519
Down there, I just followed
some guys and smuggled some goods.

00:19:34.680 --> 00:19:35.420
Smuggling?

00:19:37.700 --> 00:19:39.700
I know it's illegal.

00:19:40.559 --> 00:19:41.940
You'll surely scold me.

00:19:43.539 --> 00:19:44.160
But...

00:19:45.400 --> 00:19:47.700
But I was really pushed to the edge.

00:19:48.960 --> 00:19:51.059
Back then, I only had
one thought in my mind.

00:19:52.960 --> 00:19:54.799
Once I made the money...

00:19:55.700 --> 00:19:57.460
Once I made the money for the surgeries,

00:19:58.559 --> 00:20:00.680
I definitely quit
doing such shady businesses.

00:20:00.960 --> 00:20:02.319
Alright. It's good you're back.

00:20:03.059 --> 00:20:04.299
Many ways to make money now.

00:20:04.920 --> 00:20:06.680
Cut down on those shady businesses.

00:20:07.220 --> 00:20:08.460
I totally agree.

00:20:12.559 --> 00:20:13.220
Zhu.

00:20:14.420 --> 00:20:16.180
Enough about me. Tell me about you.

00:20:17.220 --> 00:20:20.420
While we've been away,
have you been promoted again?

00:20:21.519 --> 00:20:24.420
If you have any good news,
you have to tell us

00:20:24.500 --> 00:20:25.700
and we'll be happy for you.

00:20:26.099 --> 00:20:27.160
These past two years,

00:20:28.059 --> 00:20:29.640
I've been buried in the 6.10 case.

00:20:30.099 --> 00:20:32.672
That case is a big deal,
and the leadership takes it seriously.

00:20:32.799 --> 00:20:35.940
Both professionally and personally,
I can't give up on that case.

00:20:37.700 --> 00:20:41.940
I remember you've been
investigating this case for a long time.

00:20:43.680 --> 00:20:45.220
You still had no leads?

00:20:48.460 --> 00:20:49.920
Don't worry, Zhu.

00:20:50.960 --> 00:20:54.099
It won't help anything, right?

00:20:56.299 --> 00:20:58.420
Zhu, I'm not leaving.

00:20:58.779 --> 00:20:59.700
I'm here.

00:21:00.220 --> 00:21:04.319
If you need any help, just tell me.

00:21:05.880 --> 00:21:08.720
Now that you're back, there's
nothing much I need your help with.

00:21:09.700 --> 00:21:11.220
Just lend Qin a hand more often.

00:21:12.180 --> 00:21:13.460
These past two years,

00:21:13.960 --> 00:21:16.960
Qin handled everything
inside and out all by herself.

00:21:17.680 --> 00:21:21.059
I don't need help for now.
Tell me if you need anything.

00:21:21.799 --> 00:21:23.640
Oh, find some time

00:21:24.420 --> 00:21:25.700
to have Yonghui come see me.

00:21:25.700 --> 00:21:27.220
We will have him take a statement

00:21:27.700 --> 00:21:29.920
and see if we can track down
that hit-and-run driver.

00:21:30.460 --> 00:21:33.500
That was years ago. We can't find him.

00:21:34.059 --> 00:21:36.700
Even if we did find him and he paid up,

00:21:37.299 --> 00:21:38.799
Yonghui's arm is still useless.

00:21:40.420 --> 00:21:43.559
What worries me most now
is how he'll manage his life.

00:21:45.160 --> 00:21:46.420
That's why

00:21:47.700 --> 00:21:49.220
I want to earn more money.

00:21:50.559 --> 00:21:53.799
With more money,
things won't be so tough.

00:21:54.319 --> 00:21:56.559
True. Any ideas now?

00:21:56.960 --> 00:21:59.220
If you're stuck,
I can help you find work.

00:21:59.960 --> 00:22:00.920
Okay.

00:22:01.220 --> 00:22:03.460
I'll let you know
when I've figured it out.

00:22:03.559 --> 00:22:06.319
Alright, no need to see me off.
I'm leaving.

00:22:06.799 --> 00:22:07.779
No more drinking.

00:22:07.779 --> 00:22:08.640
No more drinking.

00:22:08.640 --> 00:22:09.559
Take care, Zhu.

00:22:22.660 --> 00:22:23.440
Guangcai.

00:22:23.660 --> 00:22:24.160
Zhu...

00:22:39.299 --> 00:22:39.799
Come on.

00:22:59.680 --> 00:23:00.299
Lijun.

00:23:00.660 --> 00:23:03.599
You took care of my family
while I was away.

00:23:05.180 --> 00:23:05.799
Besides,

00:23:07.220 --> 00:23:11.000
thanks to you for Xiaoliang's
and Mr. Chen's surgeries.

00:23:20.680 --> 00:23:21.799
I have an idea.

00:23:23.299 --> 00:23:27.000
I want to get a shopfront
at Baima Building Materials Market

00:23:27.819 --> 00:23:31.000
to start the building materials
and renovation business.

00:23:31.000 --> 00:23:32.960
You shouldn't do bookkeeping here.

00:23:33.180 --> 00:23:36.880
Let's work together
and be our own bosses in our own shop.

00:23:40.099 --> 00:23:42.680
Mr. Jiao, there's another blown fuse
over there. Go check it out.

00:23:42.960 --> 00:23:43.799
Okay, I'll be there.

00:23:52.160 --> 00:23:53.880
Wait, give me an answer.

00:23:58.380 --> 00:23:59.180
Guangcai.

00:24:00.140 --> 00:24:02.640
These two years, I was in Beiyan,
and you were in Guangnan.

00:24:03.559 --> 00:24:05.380
Did the sea breeze down there
make you stupid?

00:24:05.920 --> 00:24:07.420
What do you mean?

00:24:07.880 --> 00:24:11.599
Since we were kids,
have I ever said no to you?

00:24:12.180 --> 00:24:15.220
After two years apart,
you still want to test me?

00:24:16.660 --> 00:24:17.160
Wait!

00:24:20.059 --> 00:24:21.940
Are we not close anymore
after two years?

00:24:22.640 --> 00:24:25.220
If so, I'll turn around
and leave right now.

00:24:26.519 --> 00:24:29.420
Go ahead then.
See how you'll manage being the boss.

00:24:29.559 --> 00:24:31.059
You'll lose a lot.

00:24:34.559 --> 00:24:35.160
Come on.

00:24:36.019 --> 00:24:36.799
Sit.

00:24:44.380 --> 00:24:45.500
No more joking.

00:24:46.640 --> 00:24:49.680
I came to you for serious business.

00:24:50.059 --> 00:24:50.759
Go ahead.

00:24:51.559 --> 00:24:54.039
That Baima Building Materials Market
I just mentioned

00:24:54.660 --> 00:24:58.220
is managed by the Hao brothers who
used to work at the construction sites.

00:24:58.940 --> 00:25:00.039
Remember the Hao brothers?

00:25:02.799 --> 00:25:04.019
I've looked into it.

00:25:04.920 --> 00:25:08.759
Those two are as ruthless and greedy
as they were back in the day.

00:25:10.220 --> 00:25:13.680
So if we don't cough up some real cash,

00:25:13.960 --> 00:25:16.299
this thing won't happen.

00:25:26.720 --> 00:25:28.660
Guangcai, I think this is manageable.

00:25:29.500 --> 00:25:33.160
If you suddenly give them
a lump sum of money, it's fishy.

00:25:33.539 --> 00:25:36.059
But what if that money
came with Zhu's help?

00:25:42.920 --> 00:25:43.759
Did you get it?

00:25:44.019 --> 00:25:45.059
She'll grab it.

00:25:47.160 --> 00:25:48.180
Who's calling?

00:25:49.559 --> 00:25:50.799
Don't let him have it.

00:25:50.799 --> 00:25:51.960
- Qianqian.
- Qianqian eats.

00:25:51.960 --> 00:25:52.680
Give me a bite.

00:25:53.059 --> 00:25:53.700
- Give me a bite.
- Will you?

00:25:53.900 --> 00:25:55.559
Qianqian eats.

00:25:56.400 --> 00:25:57.559
Don't give it to him, right?

00:25:57.900 --> 00:25:58.680
Someone's knocking.

00:25:59.180 --> 00:25:59.680
Give me.

00:25:59.920 --> 00:26:00.960
- Don't throw it.
- Don't throw it.

00:26:01.140 --> 00:26:01.880
Coming.

00:26:02.160 --> 00:26:03.920
Look, aren't this kitty's eyes pretty?

00:26:08.059 --> 00:26:08.759
Zhu.

00:26:08.920 --> 00:26:09.880
Guangcai.

00:26:10.900 --> 00:26:12.839
Huifen, Guangcai's here.

00:26:12.839 --> 00:26:14.099
- Come in.
- Guangcai's here.

00:26:14.440 --> 00:26:15.059
Guangcai.

00:26:15.059 --> 00:26:15.640
Huifen.

00:26:16.279 --> 00:26:17.599
Why do you bring gifts?

00:26:17.599 --> 00:26:19.920
No, this is freshly picked peanuts
from Shaguai.

00:26:20.680 --> 00:26:22.920
Next time you come, bring no gifts.

00:26:22.920 --> 00:26:23.460
Okay.

00:26:23.460 --> 00:26:25.380
Huifen, you take Qianqian to bed.

00:26:25.380 --> 00:26:26.400
Join us later.

00:26:26.400 --> 00:26:27.039
Okay.

00:26:27.039 --> 00:26:29.140
I'm telling you, just this once.

00:26:30.059 --> 00:26:30.920
Where do I put it?

00:26:30.920 --> 00:26:31.720
I'll join you later.

00:26:32.319 --> 00:26:33.279
Go sit over there.

00:26:33.559 --> 00:26:34.200
Sit there.

00:26:34.200 --> 00:26:35.420
- Okay.
- Come on.

00:26:35.720 --> 00:26:36.380
Sit.

00:26:36.380 --> 00:26:37.059
Okay.

00:26:37.599 --> 00:26:40.099
Guangcai, why did you
bring all this stuff?

00:26:40.400 --> 00:26:42.220
You should've let me know
that you are coming.

00:26:42.559 --> 00:26:44.779
If I worked overtime,
you wouldn't see me then.

00:26:44.779 --> 00:26:46.880
No, I could also come
to check on Huifen.

00:26:48.059 --> 00:26:50.519
You didn't mention anything
about your kid last time.

00:26:50.720 --> 00:26:51.520
When?

00:26:51.968 --> 00:26:54.200
No, it's that credit union case.

00:26:54.400 --> 00:26:57.559
The officer who got shot is my comrade.
And this is his daughter.

00:26:59.099 --> 00:26:59.799
I'll do it.

00:26:59.799 --> 00:27:00.420
I...

00:27:00.420 --> 00:27:01.460
Why be polite with me?

00:27:02.440 --> 00:27:03.640
You must be up to something.

00:27:03.640 --> 00:27:05.160
Tell me, what's up?

00:27:08.880 --> 00:27:10.420
Nothing much, but...

00:27:11.519 --> 00:27:13.259
I talked it over with my family.

00:27:13.920 --> 00:27:15.400
At my age,

00:27:15.559 --> 00:27:19.019
going back to the construction site
is not feasible.

00:27:19.779 --> 00:27:21.960
Coincidentally, I ran into
a buddy from the site,

00:27:21.960 --> 00:27:23.200
a former workmate.

00:27:23.200 --> 00:27:26.380
He's a driver now, delivering goods
for the building materials market.

00:27:26.920 --> 00:27:31.140
I was thinking if I could
lease a shop and start a small business.

00:27:31.559 --> 00:27:34.680
That way, Qin wouldn't have
to follow me around everywhere.

00:27:34.920 --> 00:27:36.460
We'd settle down then.

00:27:36.460 --> 00:27:39.000
Nice! You're thinking
of starting a business?

00:27:39.900 --> 00:27:41.299
Where is the shop?

00:27:41.660 --> 00:27:43.200
Baima Building Materials Market.

00:27:43.299 --> 00:27:45.180
That is a good spot.

00:27:45.420 --> 00:27:47.839
Right now,
it's the busiest place in Beiyan.

00:27:48.279 --> 00:27:49.559
But Guangcai, I have to warn you

00:27:49.720 --> 00:27:52.680
that Baima Market is a mixed place.

00:27:53.299 --> 00:27:54.279
Are you up for it?

00:27:54.680 --> 00:27:55.680
I've been there.

00:27:56.220 --> 00:27:58.880
Some former workmates are around.
We can look out for each other.

00:27:59.559 --> 00:28:00.720
We can start small.

00:28:01.420 --> 00:28:04.799
But right now, I just don't
have enough cash on hand.

00:28:05.519 --> 00:28:07.220
That's why I came to you, Zhu.

00:28:07.759 --> 00:28:08.680
Okay, got it.

00:28:09.380 --> 00:28:11.559
But Guangcai, you know
my salary is pretty modest.

00:28:12.059 --> 00:28:14.039
Starting a business might not...

00:28:14.039 --> 00:28:16.460
Zhu, that's not what I meant.

00:28:17.140 --> 00:28:20.220
Zhu, maybe you could
help me figure something out.

00:28:20.220 --> 00:28:21.559
I need to borrow some money.

00:28:22.460 --> 00:28:25.880
I found out that if someone cosigns,

00:28:25.880 --> 00:28:27.660
we can borrow money
from the credit union.

00:28:28.019 --> 00:28:29.180
You mean a bank loan?

00:28:29.180 --> 00:28:30.279
Yes, a loan.

00:28:31.460 --> 00:28:33.180
Zhu, these cigarettes are pretty good.

00:28:33.779 --> 00:28:34.460
This works.

00:28:35.559 --> 00:28:37.460
I'll wrap them up,
and you can give them to him.

00:28:37.460 --> 00:28:39.759
No, I can't give them as a cop.

00:28:39.759 --> 00:28:42.519
When the time's right,
you slip them to him quietly.

00:28:42.759 --> 00:28:43.259
Okay.

00:28:46.319 --> 00:28:47.420
Looking sharp today!

00:28:49.380 --> 00:28:51.420
That suit looks good, very presentable.

00:28:51.640 --> 00:28:52.779
Quite the gentleman.

00:28:52.799 --> 00:28:54.299
Trying to make a good impression.

00:28:54.759 --> 00:28:56.039
I can't look shabby

00:28:56.440 --> 00:28:58.319
and tell them I want a business loan.

00:28:58.779 --> 00:28:59.960
You sit there, Guangcai.

00:29:01.299 --> 00:29:03.180
If the loan gets approved,

00:29:03.680 --> 00:29:04.680
run your business well.

00:29:05.319 --> 00:29:07.220
I know, Zhu, I've got this.

00:29:07.799 --> 00:29:10.960
Alright. Just remember to be polite
when you meet Mr. Xie later.

00:29:11.180 --> 00:29:12.059
Coming.

00:29:13.720 --> 00:29:15.220
Which one is Officer Zhu?

00:29:15.220 --> 00:29:15.799
I am.

00:29:15.799 --> 00:29:16.720
Mr. Xie, right?

00:29:17.299 --> 00:29:19.220
- Hello, Officer Zhu.
- Hello.

00:29:19.339 --> 00:29:21.180
Captain Liu told me all about you.

00:29:21.180 --> 00:29:22.700
You two are very close comrades.

00:29:22.700 --> 00:29:23.200
Yes.

00:29:24.420 --> 00:29:25.660
Please sit.

00:29:25.660 --> 00:29:26.680
- I'll sit here.
- No.

00:29:26.680 --> 00:29:27.420
You sit.

00:29:27.420 --> 00:29:27.960
Alright.

00:29:28.319 --> 00:29:29.299
You sit here.

00:29:31.160 --> 00:29:31.779
Guangcai.

00:29:32.400 --> 00:29:34.640
This is Xie Kaiyan.

00:29:35.059 --> 00:29:38.539
He's the loan officer
from Beiyan Bank's Third Branch.

00:29:39.779 --> 00:29:41.799
This is my brother, Meng Guangcai.

00:29:42.960 --> 00:29:43.720
Good to meet you.

00:29:43.720 --> 00:29:46.559
Don't be that polite.
I'm just trying to make a living.

00:29:46.940 --> 00:29:48.140
- You're too kind.
- Right.

00:29:48.220 --> 00:29:48.920
Officer Zhu.

00:29:49.059 --> 00:29:51.299
Actually, I should be
the one treating you.

00:29:51.700 --> 00:29:52.299
No, no.

00:29:52.799 --> 00:29:54.420
Waiter! Bring us your best liquor.

00:29:54.420 --> 00:29:55.920
Well, Maotai. Maotai.

00:29:56.680 --> 00:29:58.140
We'd have to go out and buy that.

00:29:58.140 --> 00:29:58.920
You...

00:29:58.920 --> 00:30:00.420
Mr. Xie, listen to me.

00:30:00.420 --> 00:30:00.920
Forget it.

00:30:00.920 --> 00:30:01.559
Regardless...

00:30:01.559 --> 00:30:02.400
Listen to me.

00:30:02.400 --> 00:30:03.259
Regardless,

00:30:03.460 --> 00:30:04.920
I'll definitely pay for this meal.

00:30:04.920 --> 00:30:05.440
Go get it.

00:30:05.440 --> 00:30:06.380
We can drink Maotai.

00:30:06.380 --> 00:30:07.759
If not, this one will do.

00:30:07.759 --> 00:30:08.420
We're waiting.

00:30:08.720 --> 00:30:10.400
Mr. Xie, let's get down to business.

00:30:10.640 --> 00:30:12.140
Well, Liu Hua

00:30:12.140 --> 00:30:14.819
should have told you about it.

00:30:15.759 --> 00:30:18.380
You're the expert
on bank loan approvals.

00:30:18.640 --> 00:30:20.059
Today, please help assess

00:30:20.059 --> 00:30:23.220
whether my brother
meets the requirements

00:30:23.319 --> 00:30:25.779
and gets a loan from you.

00:30:26.180 --> 00:30:27.279
Come on!

00:30:27.880 --> 00:30:31.279
If Captain Liu is involved,
it has to be approved.

00:30:31.279 --> 00:30:31.960
Don't say that.

00:30:32.759 --> 00:30:35.559
Let's be clear.
We must follow the rules.

00:30:35.759 --> 00:30:37.700
We'll go through the proper procedures.

00:30:38.559 --> 00:30:40.880
Zhu, Mr. Xie,
shall we talk while we eat?

00:30:40.880 --> 00:30:41.460
- Okay?
- Sure.

00:30:41.460 --> 00:30:42.160
Let me.

00:30:42.160 --> 00:30:42.960
You open the bottle.

00:30:42.960 --> 00:30:43.960
Let's start with this

00:30:43.960 --> 00:30:45.019
and wait for the Maotai.

00:30:45.019 --> 00:30:46.960
No need. This is fine. This is fine.

00:30:49.059 --> 00:30:50.759
I know about this.

00:30:50.759 --> 00:30:53.220
It's about construction
and building materials.

00:30:53.220 --> 00:30:55.140
- Yes.
- Great prospects there.

00:30:55.140 --> 00:30:58.099
So this shop belongs to him

00:30:58.099 --> 00:31:00.019
or you?

00:31:00.160 --> 00:31:01.440
This has nothing to do with me.

00:31:01.440 --> 00:31:02.559
The specifics

00:31:02.559 --> 00:31:04.400
are mainly for you two to discuss.

00:31:06.059 --> 00:31:08.880
So Officer Liu and this shop...

00:31:10.279 --> 00:31:11.299
Mr. Xie, listen.

00:31:11.559 --> 00:31:14.299
We police officers
can't do this kind of thing.

00:31:14.299 --> 00:31:15.440
Regulations forbid it.

00:31:15.920 --> 00:31:19.440
Liu Hua is my police academy classmate
We're very close.

00:31:19.660 --> 00:31:22.819
I asked him to introduce you to us.

00:31:26.680 --> 00:31:27.559
Got it.

00:31:28.299 --> 00:31:28.799
Got it.

00:31:29.400 --> 00:31:30.180
Have some food.

00:31:30.180 --> 00:31:31.180
Come on.

00:31:31.299 --> 00:31:32.819
Fate brings us here.

00:31:32.819 --> 00:31:33.880
Let's have a drink.

00:31:33.880 --> 00:31:35.599
No. I have duty later.

00:31:35.599 --> 00:31:36.680
So I can't drink.

00:31:36.960 --> 00:31:37.819
Strict rules.

00:31:37.819 --> 00:31:38.799
Right.

00:31:38.799 --> 00:31:40.720
Then he can drink.

00:31:40.880 --> 00:31:42.220
He can handle his liquor.

00:31:42.220 --> 00:31:43.440
Yes, he can.

00:31:43.559 --> 00:31:44.180
Come on.

00:31:44.180 --> 00:31:44.759
Cheers.

00:31:45.180 --> 00:31:46.180
Okay.

00:31:46.779 --> 00:31:47.299
Thank you.

00:31:47.299 --> 00:31:48.640
- Here, to you.
- I'll have tea.

00:31:49.000 --> 00:31:50.660
Anything can do.

00:31:50.660 --> 00:31:51.539
To you.

00:31:54.339 --> 00:31:55.019
(Resolving your worries)
I'll go back.

00:31:55.420 --> 00:31:56.180
(Securing your bright future)
Take care, goodbye.

00:32:15.380 --> 00:32:16.039
Mr. Xie.

00:32:16.880 --> 00:32:17.799
Mr. Xie!

00:32:18.279 --> 00:32:19.519
Mr. Xie, it's me, Guangcai.

00:32:20.299 --> 00:32:22.920
Last week, we had a meal
with Officer Zhu.

00:32:23.660 --> 00:32:25.460
Remember? We agreed

00:32:25.460 --> 00:32:27.420
on my loan.

00:32:27.599 --> 00:32:28.440
I'm Guangcai.

00:32:32.200 --> 00:32:33.259
Guangcai, right?

00:32:34.259 --> 00:32:35.960
Why did you come all the way here?

00:32:36.519 --> 00:32:37.819
It's nothing.

00:32:38.059 --> 00:32:39.940
I called you before,

00:32:39.940 --> 00:32:42.176
and the reception
always said you weren't in the office.

00:32:42.299 --> 00:32:44.180
I worried if you called back,
I might miss it.

00:32:44.259 --> 00:32:45.940
So I came to you today

00:32:45.940 --> 00:32:48.099
to ask about the loan.

00:32:48.279 --> 00:32:50.920
I submitted your loan application.

00:32:50.920 --> 00:32:52.299
Waiting for the approval.

00:32:53.440 --> 00:32:55.960
You know loans are tight right now.

00:32:56.400 --> 00:32:58.039
I even got criticized over your case.

00:32:58.039 --> 00:33:00.500
We can't just loan to anyone. Right?

00:33:01.019 --> 00:33:02.400
Right, how much do you want?

00:33:03.420 --> 00:33:04.319
A hundred thousand.

00:33:05.039 --> 00:33:07.059
No chance then.
At most, thirty thousand.

00:33:07.599 --> 00:33:09.599
Alright, go home and wait for news.

00:33:09.599 --> 00:33:11.180
No rush. Procedures take time.

00:33:11.640 --> 00:33:12.940
Well, Mr. Xie.

00:33:13.099 --> 00:33:15.180
This is that liquor you like.

00:33:18.019 --> 00:33:20.039
What? What do you mean?

00:33:20.039 --> 00:33:21.960
- Take it away.
- And this.

00:33:22.440 --> 00:33:23.039
Mr. Xie.

00:33:25.420 --> 00:33:28.160
This phone is the latest model.
They say it's great.

00:33:30.420 --> 00:33:31.460
About this...

00:33:32.319 --> 00:33:33.420
Wait, Guangcai.

00:33:33.420 --> 00:33:34.559
You shouldn't do this.

00:33:34.559 --> 00:33:35.940
I'm not blaming you,

00:33:35.940 --> 00:33:37.539
we're friends now.

00:33:37.539 --> 00:33:38.700
Why do this?

00:33:40.299 --> 00:33:42.779
Alright, I'll bring it up
with my supervisor

00:33:42.779 --> 00:33:45.000
- Okay.
- and see if we can get your loan amount

00:33:45.000 --> 00:33:45.940
increased a bit.

00:33:46.200 --> 00:33:48.799
I'll speed up the procedures, okay?

00:33:48.799 --> 00:33:49.720
Okay.

00:33:49.720 --> 00:33:50.660
Wait for my update.

00:33:50.660 --> 00:33:51.160
Okay.

00:33:51.160 --> 00:33:51.660
Don't worry.

00:33:51.660 --> 00:33:54.048
Once I get this loan approved,
I'll do things right.

00:33:54.176 --> 00:33:55.500
Don't worry, we're friends now.

00:33:55.500 --> 00:33:56.220
Look at you.

00:33:56.720 --> 00:33:57.220
Don't worry.

00:33:57.220 --> 00:33:58.059
Thank you, Mr. Xie.

00:33:58.059 --> 00:33:58.559
Don't worry.

00:33:58.660 --> 00:33:59.299
Take care.

00:34:01.160 --> 00:34:02.180
Wait for my updates.

00:34:10.219 --> 00:34:10.900
Hongkang.

00:34:11.258 --> 00:34:11.780
(Hao Hongkang, eldest of the Hao
brothers managing Baima Market)

00:34:11.780 --> 00:34:12.300
(Hao Hongliang, youngest of the Hao
brothers managing Baima Market)

00:34:12.300 --> 00:34:13.599
This is seventy thousand yuan.

00:34:14.099 --> 00:34:16.519
Sixty thousands is for the storefront.

00:34:16.599 --> 00:34:19.719
The other ten thousand
is a little token from the three of us.

00:34:26.000 --> 00:34:27.300
Clever move, Guangcai.

00:34:28.840 --> 00:34:30.039
You've got the hang of it.

00:34:32.219 --> 00:34:35.340
If you guys hadn't suddenly
run off to Guangnan before,

00:34:35.719 --> 00:34:39.260
maybe you'd be the head today.

00:34:40.000 --> 00:34:42.179
No way. Impossible!

00:34:42.860 --> 00:34:46.219
The three of us just want
to learn how to do business

00:34:46.219 --> 00:34:48.500
from you two brothers in the market.

00:34:50.500 --> 00:34:52.800
Learning anything
requires paying tuition, right?

00:34:52.800 --> 00:34:53.800
Sweet talker.

00:34:55.039 --> 00:34:57.000
Look, this is about the business, right?

00:34:57.360 --> 00:34:59.719
So we have to tell you the truth first.

00:35:00.199 --> 00:35:03.719
I can show you the ropes,
but the rest is up to you.

00:35:04.659 --> 00:35:06.400
The storefront is yours.

00:35:07.519 --> 00:35:10.380
But whether the business succeeds or not

00:35:10.380 --> 00:35:12.340
depends on you guys.

00:35:13.559 --> 00:35:14.539
That's great!

00:35:14.539 --> 00:35:16.860
Hey, Lijun, Dazhu.
Come on, let's toast them again.

00:35:16.860 --> 00:35:18.719
Hold on, I'm not done.

00:35:19.840 --> 00:35:23.199
Listen, anyone who gets
a storefront in this market

00:35:23.559 --> 00:35:25.380
is a good buddy to us.

00:35:26.340 --> 00:35:29.300
So we have our own rules.

00:35:30.199 --> 00:35:31.619
For the first two years,

00:35:32.619 --> 00:35:33.860
we have to take this amount.

00:35:38.519 --> 00:35:39.340
Four thousand?

00:35:51.800 --> 00:35:52.659
Forty thousand?

00:35:53.619 --> 00:35:55.119
Forty thousand?

00:35:55.659 --> 00:35:57.619
Profit. 40 percent of the profits.

00:35:58.760 --> 00:36:00.360
What? 40 percent?

00:36:00.519 --> 00:36:01.400
What's wrong with you?

00:36:02.019 --> 00:36:02.519
Don't shout.

00:36:02.519 --> 00:36:03.780
You scared me!

00:36:04.019 --> 00:36:04.719
Calm.

00:36:05.099 --> 00:36:06.500
Buddy! He's had too much to drink.

00:36:06.639 --> 00:36:08.280
Let's discuss the cut.

00:36:08.559 --> 00:36:09.059
Please sit.

00:36:09.059 --> 00:36:10.860
Nonsense! Who's your buddy?

00:36:11.159 --> 00:36:12.219
40 percent.

00:36:12.500 --> 00:36:14.039
Heard that? Take it or leave it.

00:36:14.219 --> 00:36:15.679
If you don't agree, leave.

00:36:15.679 --> 00:36:16.280
Let's go.

00:36:16.280 --> 00:36:17.179
- Hongliang.
- Go.

00:36:18.280 --> 00:36:19.320
I'll see you out.

00:36:19.320 --> 00:36:20.440
Stop being so arrogant.

00:36:22.579 --> 00:36:23.760
Don't be mad, Hongkang.

00:36:23.760 --> 00:36:25.079
I'll see you out. Come on.

00:36:25.079 --> 00:36:25.860
I'll see you out.

00:36:28.619 --> 00:36:31.559
What's wrong with you?
We were still negotiating.

00:36:31.559 --> 00:36:32.360
What did you do?

00:36:32.360 --> 00:36:35.079
Is this negotiation? This is robbery!

00:36:35.440 --> 00:36:36.800
There's no turning back.

00:36:37.860 --> 00:36:40.119
Look at their attitude.
Even if we back out now,

00:36:40.119 --> 00:36:41.619
think we'll get our money back?

00:36:41.840 --> 00:36:43.300
Do you want to haul bricks?

00:36:43.400 --> 00:36:43.900
Guangcai.

00:36:44.000 --> 00:36:45.719
At worst, we can leave Beiyan.

00:36:46.079 --> 00:36:47.380
We have money.

00:36:47.380 --> 00:36:48.780
Can't you watch your mouth?

00:36:49.519 --> 00:36:50.300
Sit down!

00:36:56.320 --> 00:36:57.619
I've said it many times.

00:36:58.000 --> 00:36:59.619
Don't keep bringing up leaving.

00:37:02.300 --> 00:37:03.559
Why were you on a temper?

00:37:07.059 --> 00:37:10.139
We can't go back to living
like before, understand?

00:37:15.760 --> 00:37:17.340
Then let me ask you, Guangcai.

00:37:17.340 --> 00:37:19.820
Are we just going
to let him rob our money?

00:37:19.820 --> 00:37:21.199
Who said that?

00:37:22.380 --> 00:37:26.059
Once our business is up,
let's see how long he can do this.

00:37:35.700 --> 00:37:40.724
=The Silent Rift=